Exxaro Calls For Offers For ‘Non-Core’ Assets It’s Selling in South Africa

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-05-05T05:22:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/exxaro-calls-for-offers-for-non-core-assets-it-s-selling-in-south-africa.html
Exxaro Resources Ltd. (EXX)  called for
expressions of interest in “non-core” coal assets it’s selling
in  South Africa .  Exxaro will sell prospecting rights at Arnot South,
Kranspan and Vaalbult in Mpumalanga province, the Johannesburg-
based company said in an advertisement published in  Business
Report  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  